  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the effect of nocturnal administration of
      Anti-hypertensive medications in Non-dippers.

      Efficacy variables.

        1. ECHO

        2. 24hr. horter

        3. IMT

        4. BUN/crea, urine analysis (microalbulinuria

        5. Cardio vascular event. &quot;
    </textblock>
